  <brief_title>Has Pulmonary Rehabilitation a Positive Impact on Sleep Quality in Patients Suffering From COPD ?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Has Pulmonary Rehabilitation a Positive Impact on Sleep Quality in Patients Suffering From Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease?</official_title>
